        <div class="sm:mb-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">Ready to take your business to
                    the next level? </h1><br />
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">Get Started Today! Start
                    using UnityBiz today and experience the difference. Our platform is
                    designed to help you succeed, one task at a time. Discover UnityBiz –
                    Your Unified Business Solution!</p>
                <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
                    {{#if logged_in}}
